    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="268733313">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-268733313" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-268733313" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="268733313">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/freeyou/">ming</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2010-07-09</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">就像以前某电视观众说的，易通过这种通俗性的故事介绍一些古代社会的基本常识，还是很值得肯定的。</p>
        </div>
